信じてくれる人がいる
There are people who believe in me.

55
00:07:21,888 --> 00:07:26,788
この歌で君と繋がっていられる
Through this song, I can stay connected with you.

56
00:07:26,788 --> 00:07:31,988
忘れられないストーリー 描いていこう
Let's draw an unforgettable story together.

57
00:07:31,988 --> 00:07:32,488
行くよ！
Here we go!

58
00:07:33,088 --> 00:07:35,588
世界一かわいい
World's cutest,

59
00:07:35,588 --> 00:07:38,088
宇宙一かわいい
universe's cutest.

60
